{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-markdown-remark-js","path":"/hitchhikers-guide/apps/docs/content/argocd-gitops/get_access_to_argocd.md","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Operate First"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"1c6092a0-9c6f-5b50-9640-54e0a66e40da","html":"<h1 id=\"get-access-to-argocd\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#get-access-to-argocd\" aria-label=\"get access to argocd permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Get access to ArgoCD</h1>\n<p>To get access to the Operate First ArgoCD instance (found <a href=\"https://argocd.operate-first.cloud\">here</a>), you need to belong to an OpenShift <code class=\"language-text\">Group</code> that has\naccess to an <code class=\"language-text\">ArgoCD Project</code>. You can find which groups have access by checking the contents of <a href=\"https://github.com/operate-first/apps/blob/master/argocd/overlays/moc-infra/configs/argo_cm/dex.config\">this file</a>.</p>\n<p>If your OCP <code class=\"language-text\">Group</code> is not listed here then please follow <a href=\"onboarding_to_argocd.md\">these instructions</a> to get your team\nonboarded.</p>\n<p>If your team is already onboarded to ArgoCD (and thuse listed in <code class=\"language-text\">dex.config</code>) but you are not in it, then please follow\n<a href=\"../cluster-scope/add_user_to_group.md\">these instructions</a> to get added to your team.</p>","fields":{"srcLink":"https://github.com/operate-first/apps/blob/master/docs/content/argocd-gi